<li>Prix <a href="/wiki/Kurt_Tucholsky" title="Kurt Tucholsky">Kurt Tucholsky</a> (1996)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Prix_Herder" title="Prix Herder">Prix Herder</a> (1999)</li>
